---
title: "US14 — Sync phone sensors / wearables"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ActiveWorkoutScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ActiveWorkout
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>WorkoutDataSource (PhoneSensorSource)
  A->>B: workout running
  B->>C: live state
  C->>G: start() — geolocator + pedometer
  loop every sensor tick
    G-->>C: distance, steps, track point
    C-->>B: live metrics
    B-->>A: DISTANCE / PACE update
  end
  note over G: wearables later = new<br/>HealthSource / BleHeartRateSource class
